---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🧑‍🚀 Pick my thoughts - The hows and The whys</h1>
			<p>
			This space is where I share practical lessons from the work I do across cloud infrastructure, security, automation, and emerging AI systems.
			</p><p>
			The blogs I publish here explore the thinking behind real technical decisions: why certain risks matter, how problems are identified, and what goes into hardening, mitigating, monitoring, and logging modern environments.
			</p><p>
			For confidentiality and security reasons, I do not share sensitive implementation details. Instead, I focus on the transferable process: the reasoning, architecture choices, lessons learned, and security practices that help protect cloud infrastructure, CI/CD pipelines, MCP servers, and AI agents.
			</p><p>
			My goal is to document how I think, how I solve problems, and how I continue growing as a cloud and security professional.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
